During the period between 5-11 Apr 2017, Hebei province reported 7 human H7N9 AIV cases from the following areas [only 6 are listed below. - Mod.LM]:

- Cangzhou:
1. a 33-year-old male, [presented with] severe pneumonia;
2. 83-year-old male;
3. 50-year-old female;
4. 47-year-old male.

- Baoding: 38-year-old male case

- Bazhou: 65-year-old male case

